recentActivity.message: Fix typo in Dioxus CLI installation command

Update Dioxus build config and remove unused assets

The commit consolidates several Dioxus-related changes including
removing Bun from the deploy workflow, optimizing build profiles, and
cleaning up unused assets.

Improve GitHub Actions caching and installation steps

The updated workflow caches more paths, adds better cache keys, and
skips redundant tool installations. This should speed up builds by
reducing unnecessary downloads and compilations.
Update Cloudflare project name and add Firebase analytics

Update deployment workflow for Dioxus build

The build command no longer needs SSG flag and artifact names are
corrected to match Dioxus instead of Next.js. Firebase project ID is
also updated.

Configure multi-platform deployment setup

This commit sets up automated deployment to GitHub Pages, Cloudflare
Pages and Firebase Hosting via GitHub Actions workflow. It also includes
Firebase configuration files and some minor CSS cleanup.
Add fade transition to Ather canvas animation
Adjust filter button size and hover effect dimensions
